<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-discover-hidden-pocket-in-cancer-promoting-enzyme/">Mayo Clinic researchers discover &amp;#8216;hidden pocket&amp;#8217; in cancer-promoting enzyme</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
