		<title>Mayo Clinic researchers find &amp;#8216;sugar coating&amp;#8217; cells can protect those typically destroyed in type 1 diabetes</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-find-sugar-coating-cells-can-protect-those-typically-destroyed-in-type-1-diabetes/</link>
		
